embeds.title: TheFishyGamer11
embeds.description:
Heyo, I’m Camdyn, I’m 16, and Chrome OS is one of my passions. I help users & moderate for three different platforms on Chrome OS. I love working with technology, it has been one of my hobbies for years to work for hours on (and even just play games, mostly competitive).

I have never purchased a Chromebook before, all of my technology and skill are essentially received through my school district.
